    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《Limbot》，这是一款最多支持 4 名玩家一起操控穿着巨大纸板机器人服装的人的物理乱斗游戏，在城市里横冲直撞。整座纸艺都市天生就是给你碾碎、踩扁、砸成纸屑的！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在城市里尽情踩踏！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335510/extras/19db2e0739cbf9298be4a6027a0971c7.poster.avif?t=1769005299\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335510/extras/19db2e0739cbf9298be4a6027a0971c7.webm?t=1769005299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335510/extras/19db2e0739cbf9298be4a6027a0971c7.mp4?t=1769005299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踩、踢、挥拳，一路完成各种离谱的目标。这里是一整个可完全破坏的纸板世界，每栋建筑、每个障碍、每个敌人，都能被你砸得粉碎或者压成纸浆！推倒摩天大楼，正面迎战纸片敌人，再把这个世界里最大也最滑稽的手工 Boss 统统打趴下……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335510/extras/ff202011ce488d45dc7f111b027184e5.poster.avif?t=1769005299\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335510/extras/ff202011ce488d45dc7f111b027184e5.webm?t=1769005299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335510/extras/ff202011ce488d45dc7f111b027184e5.mp4?t=1769005299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>用胶带和汽水罐强化自己！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发挥你的 DIY 灵感，解锁各种升级来改造机器人，比如在小腿上绑个汽水罐获得实用的加速效果，用木勺拉长空手道劈砍的攻击距离，或者贴满贴纸单纯为了更有范儿。把这些古怪的零件随意组合，做出只属于你的完美机器人！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>操控机器人，从未这么轻松！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335510/extras/bc221f72a99a0d39ea340c3ca952cff7.poster.avif?t=1769005299\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335510/extras/bc221f72a99a0d39ea340c3ca952cff7.webm?t=1769005299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3335510/extras/bc221f72a99a0d39ea340c3ca952cff7.mp4?t=1769005299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直观的操作方式让挥动四肢变得简单易上手，不同年龄和水平的玩家都能很快参与进来。你真正需要搞明白的，是怎么和队友配合……祝你好运。对了还有一件事，如果机器人摔倒了，那肯定是你队友的锅。</p>",
